CRITICAL Astro WebContainer Rules:
- package.json MUST have "type": "module"
- astro.config.mjs uses ESM exports
- ALWAYS use `npm run dev` to start â€” never use bare `astro dev`
- Pages go in src/pages/ directory (file-based routing)
- Components go in src/components/
- Layouts go in src/layouts/
- Astro components use .astro extension with frontmatter (---) blocks
